                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9703" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1458</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">777 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">A建筑公司的税收筹划破局之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The Breakthrough of Tax Planning for A Construction Company</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">马成慧，钱诗睿，段文轩，蒋德良，钟捷麒，赵茂，杨霞，康萍，宁德节</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">云南师范大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">云南建投第三建设有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">建筑、建材业与房地产业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">税收筹划；建筑公司；纳税风险</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Tax planning; Construction companies; Tax risk</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例主要描述云南A建筑公司在X学校建设项目中进行税收筹划的历程。A建筑公司作为云南省国有独资骨干企业，承接了规模庞大的X学校建设项目，该项目是云南省“四个一百”建设项目以及丽江市2022年度市级重点项目，对加快滇西北基础教育硬件设施建设步伐、推动云南省教育事业高质量发展具有重要意义。但在项目实施过程中，A公司面临着税负较高，财务压力较大，进项税抵扣不足以及人力成本占比较高等诸多难题。面对这些难题，公司组建了专业的税收筹划团队，深入研究国家以及地方税收政策，通过拆分合同、明确各环节价款及适用税率、规划采购付款时点、加强供应商管理和与劳务公司合作等一系列举措来进行税收筹划。随着税收筹划方案逐步落实，公司在降低税负、优化现金流、分散风险等方面效果显著。本案例展示了A建筑公司从面临困局到成功破局的整个过程，旨在引导学生对增值税计算、税收筹划方法、供应商激励机制以及关注涉税风险等方面进行深入思考。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case focuses on the tax planning process of A Construction Company of Yunnan Province in the construction project for School X. As a wholly state-owned key enterprise in Yunnan Province, the X school construction project undertaken by the company is large-scale, which is the &quot;four hundred&quot; construction project in Yunnan Province and the 2022 municipal key project of Lijiang City, which is of great significance for accelerating the pace of construction of basic education hardware facilities in northwest Yunnan and promoting the high-quality development of education in Yunnan Province. However, in the constructive of the project, the company encountered many problems such as high tax burden, high financial pressure, insufficient input tax deduction, and high labor costs. To improve the situation, the company set up a professional tax planning team to study the local and national tax policies in-depth and then implementing the tax planning through a series of measures such as contract splitting to clarify the price and tax rate of each link, optimizing the purchase payment time, enhancing supplier management, and cooperating with labor companies etc. With the gradual implementation of the tax planning plan, the company has achieved remarkable results in reducing tax burden, optimizing cash flow and diversifying risks. The case displays the entire process of how construction company resolves the dilemma. It aims to guide students to explore deeply about VAT calculation, tax planning methods, supplier incentive mechanisms and prevention of tax-related risks.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《税法》、《企业税务筹划》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">税收筹划；供应商管理；营业利润</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-07</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
